Lloyds May Not Give Former CEO Daniels 2011 Bonus, Times Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-15T00:30:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/lloyds-may-not-give-former-ceo-daniels-2011-bonus-times-reports.html
  Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY)  may be
close to ruling out paying former Chief Executive Officer  Eric
Daniels  a bonus for this year after shareholders objected to
such a payment, the London-based Times reported, without saying
where it got the information.     Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
